Parts-$329.99
Labour-$594.83 (3.5 hours x $169.95/h)
Deductible-$100.00 + tax 
Tax-$107.23
Authorization-KLU37JQX34

Total = $932.04

Once the repair is complete, please send us a copy of the final invoice for payment.

Best regards, 

Matthew Puls
Claims Adjuster

notes.note: Brandon from Seaway GM called, said they also need the blower motor resistor now. Inquired about if the blower motor was even needed in the first place, as it sounded like they replaced the blower motor and it did not correct the issue. Brandon confirmed the technician bypassed power to the blower motor initially, and was having issues getting the blower to work due to an internal short. Once the blower was replaced and power was restored, still had issues with fan working intermittently, which was diagnosed as the resistor. Authorizing additional part. M.P.
